+5s say speaker="Lloyd McKenzie" text="Excellent. We covered a lot of ground today. Irma, Gay — thank you for joining from PA. This was productive."
+2s say speaker="Irma Jongeneel" text="Very productive. We'll bring the $match updates to the PA call on Wednesday."
